name: Supergalactic Fall Control Squad
description:
Welcome welcome, all of you, get close to experiment that anyone never seen before and with that get acess to join the Supergalactic Fall Control Squad, with us you will participate in adventures and rescue missons to save thousends and thousends types of life in the most advanced spaceships.

We were afiliated with the most powerfull empires of all over the universe and realitys but not just the powerfull, dont worry, we were thogether with the small ones too, if someone needs help we WILL be there.

Play this simulation and with many points you can join Supergalactic Fall Control Squad right now.
